# Stray dev-VM symlink to the souffle reference tarball cache. The L2
# runner used to fall back to this path (CACHE_PATCH_v1, since scrubbed)
# and a symlink may still be left at the repo root on long-lived dev
# VMs. Ignore it so a fresh clone-or-fetch doesn't surface it as
# untracked. The L2 runner today downloads from HuggingFace; the
# /datasets/souffle_ref_tarballs/ cache (if any) is consulted via
# /datasets/lib/patch_repo.py on dev VMs only, not via this symlink.
/souffle_ref_tarballs

